void testRandomFlow() { ... }
```

# @Nested ğŸ“‚

Group tests hierachically for better reports.

```java
class AccountTest {
    @Nested
    class WhenNew {
        @Test void balanceIsZero() { ... }
    }
}
```

# assertTimeout â±ï¸

Fail if code takes too long.

```java
assertTimeout(Duration.ofMillis(500), () -> {
    // some time consuming task
});
```

